name: grilled salmon with avocados & tomato vinaigrette
instructions:
1. In small bowl, whisk together olive oil, vinegar and honey. 

2. Dice tomato and parsley and add to vinaigrette. 

3. Add thyme. Season to taste with salt and pepper. 

4. Heat grill pan or gas or charcoal grill.

5. Season salmon to taste with salt and pepper.

6. Grill 8-10 minutes, depending on thickness. Turn carefully with a wide spatula and grill 8-10 minutes more or until flesh of salmon flakes easily.

7. Slice avocado and place on salmon filet. Spoon vinaigrette over salmon.
